						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"name\": \"Audio-Technica AT899cH Omni Lavalier Microphone\",\n    \"type\": \"physical\",\n    \"weight\": 0.42,\n    \"price\": 179,\n    \"sku\": \"25944_base\",\n    \"brand_name\": \"Audio-Technica\",\n    \"custom_url\": {\n        \"url\": \"/item/25944\"\n    },\n    \"categories\": [\n        716\n    ],\n    \"description\": \"<p>The AT899 subminiature omnidirectional microphone is engineered for intelligible, accurate voice reproduction. Its low-profile design (a mere 5 mm in diameter) assures minimum visibility. The mic may be worn as a lavalier and is easily hidden in clothing or hair. Includes a clothing clip, viper clip, magnet clip and lanyard, two windscreens, two element covers, three single mic holders, and two double mic holders.</p>  <p>For interviews, documentary, film and theatre applications. With AT8537 power module and AT899AK accessory kit. Audio-Technicaï¿½s omnidirectional AT899 is engineered for intelligible, accurate voice reproduction. Its low-profile design (a mere 5mm in diameter) assures minimum visibility. The mic may be worn as a lavalier and is easily hidden in clothing or hair. It offers the convenience of battery or phantom power; its switchable low-frequency roll-off reduces popping.</p>  <h2>Microphone Features</h2> <ul> <li>Maximum intelligibility and clean, accurate reproduction for vocalists, lecturers, stage and television talent, and houses of worship</li> <li>Low-profile design (a mere 5 mm in diameter) is ideal for applications requiring minimum visibility</li> <li>Operates on battery or phantom power</li> <li>Extensive array of provided accessories includes a clothing clip, viper clip, magnet clip and lanyard (black models only), windscreens, element covers, interchangeable single and double mic holders</li> <li>Accessories available separately include complete accessory kits, clothing clips, three-pack element covers and three-pack windscreens</li> <li>9.8' (3.0 m) cable permanently attached to mic, TA3F connector at power module</li> </ul> \",\n    \"custom_fields\": [\n        {\n            \"name\": \"Attatchments\",\n            \"value\": \"[{\\\"file\\\":\\\"AT899_Datasheet.pdf\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"AT899 Data Sheet\\\"}]\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"meta_keywords\": [\n        \"Audio-Technica AT899cH Omni Lavalier Microphone\",\n        \" Black\"\n    ],\n    \"meta_description\": \"Audio-Technica AT899cH Omni Lavalier Microphone, Black\",\n    \"variants\": [\n        {\n            \"sku\": \"25944\",\n            \"mpn\": \"AT899cH\",\n            \"image_url\": \"https://soundpro.com/catalog/items/at899ch.jpg\",\n            \"price\": 179,\n            \"weight\": 0.42,\n            \"option_values\": [\n                {\n                    \"option_display_name\": \"Color\",\n                    \"label\": \"Black\",\n                    \"is_default\":true\n                }\n            ]\n        },\n        {\n            \"sku\": \"25959\",\n            \"mpn\": \"AT899cH-TH\",\n            \"image_url\": \"https://soundpro.com/catalog/items/at899ch-th.jpg\",\n            \"price\": 179,\n            \"weight\": 0.42,\n            \"option_values\": [\n                {\n                    \"option_display_name\": \"Color\",\n                    \"label\": \"Beige\"\n                }\n            ]\n        }\n    ]\n}",
